status":"done","startedAt":1775992492604,"endedAt":1775992560577,"runtimeMs":67973,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5163901258","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ba02d9fc-7f3e-47b8-8f69-6edd7f634a5d.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have comprehensive data. Let me compile the full report for Khuowgn. I can see:\n\n1. **Confluence specs**: OTLXPA1 space has detailed requirements for:\n   - Lead Management (2.1) - CRUD, filtering, status tracking\n   - Teacher evaluation of students - rating system (1-5 stars), comments\n   - Exam schedules\n   - Various other modules\n\n2. **Backend commits** (recent - March 2026):\n   - Auth token migration to httpOnly cookies\n   - Swagger API documentation overhaul\n   - env.helper.ts centralization\n   - Response format standardization (IMeta)\n   - Docker/Dockerfile improvements\n   - Payment & User response standardization\n   - Open MR !166: Clean architecture migration (Phase 1 - presentation/api layer)\n\n3. **Frontend commits** (recent - March 2026):\n   - API v1 prefix synchronization\n   - loginByTokenApi fix\n   - Docker compose fixes\n   - Lint fixes\n   - Indentation standardization (2-space)\n\n4. **Overall status**:\n   - Backend: In active refactoring phase, migration to clean architecture in progress\n   - Frontend: API sync work, bug fixes\n   - The project appears to be actively developed\n\nLet me now create a comprehensive summary report."},{"type":"text","text":"Tôi đã thu thập đầy đủ dữ liệu từ **Confluence (OTLXPA1)** + **GitLab**. Dưới đây là báo cáo tổng hợp:\n\n---\n\n## 📋 BÁO CÁO TỔNG HỢP — AHV DTLX\n\n### 1. YÊU CẦU DỰ ÁN (Confluence — OTLXPA1)\n\n| Module | Trạng thái | Mô tả |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Quản lý Leads** | ✅ ACTIVE | CRUD, lọc theo ngày/sale/mức độ quan tâm, trạng thái: Mới/Đã liên hệ/Chuyển đổi/Mất/Đóng |\n| **Giáo viên đánh giá HV** | ✅ ACTIVE | Rating 1-5 sao, nhận xét buổi học, filter theo GV/KHóa/HV |\n| **Lịch thi sát hạch** | ✅ ACTIVE | Quản lý lịch thi OTO |\n| **Xếp hạng giáo viên** | ✅ ACTIVE | Ranking teachers |\n| **Tra cứu GPLX** | ✅ ACTIVE | Tra cứu giấy phép lái xe |\n\n---\n\n### 2. BACKEND (`ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend`) — 30 commits gần nhất\n\n**Tình trạng: 🔄 Đang refactor mạnh (tháng 3/2026)**\n\n| STT | Commit | Tác giả | Mô tả |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | `e3887cf` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | **Auth token → httpOnly cookies** (bảo mật) |\n| 2 | `92606250` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | Swagger rewrite đầy đủ, CSP fix SwaggerUI, IMeta standardization |\n| 3 | `49f91b98` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | **env.helper.ts** thay thế environment.ts — tập trung config |\n| 4 | `15279ed5` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | Docker/Docker-compose update |\n| 5 | `afc5983d` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | Fix lint |\n| 6 | `da42f507` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | Swagger: CRUD paths cho studentComments, teacherComments, studentInfos, teacherInfos |\n| 7 | `c053e5a2` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | MR !155: Auth token → secure cookies |\n| 8 | `3b3961b0` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | Swagger: xóa duplicate paths/schemas (-452 lines) |\n| 9 | `e07b4d22` | Ninh Thanh Khuong | MR !158: Route sửa đổi (course, courseStudent, leadInfos, userRoles) |\n| 10 | `2e7fa611` | Hiếu Phạm Minh | MR !160: Đổi project folder trên host |\n\n**🔴 Open MR !166** — `feature/clean-architecture-migration` → `refactor/main`\n> *Phase 1: Restructure routes into `src/presentation/api/` layer. Đang chờ merge.*\n\n**Các thành tựu chính:**\n- ✅ Token auth chuyển sang httpOnly cookies (XSS protection)\n- ✅ Swagger API docs hoàn chỉnh, loại bỏ trùng lặp\n- ✅ env.helper.ts centralized environment config\n- ✅ Payment & User response chuẩn hóa IMeta interface\n- ✅ Dockerfile/Docker-compose tối ưu\n- 🔄 Clean architecture migration đang tiến hành\n\n---\n\n### 3. FRONTEND (`ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-frontend`) — 30 commits gần nhất\n\n**Tình trạng: 🔄 Sync & Fix (tháng 3/2026)**\n\n| STT | Commit | Tác giả | Mô tả |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | `53263472` | hieupm | **User profile persistence via localStorage** (thay /auth/me) |\n| 2 | `d0b28980` | hieupm | **MR !96: Khôi phục loginByTokenApi** sau backend refactor |\n| 3 | `36a3faae` | hieupm | **Comprehensive API sync** — thêm `/v1` prefix + pluralization |\n| 4 | `3f2ac6df` | hieupm | Đổi project folder |\n| 5 | `a1defd2c` | hieupm | Fix lint, suppress hook warnings |\n| 6 | `5b3c6531` | hieupm | 2-space indentation toàn bộ project |\n| 7 | `ae63e278` | Mai Chien | MR !88: **Stadium calendar edit hotfix** |\n| 8 | `3300a3a7` | Mai Chien | Hotfix edit stadium calendar |\n| 9 | `f5078e02` | Mai Chien | Fix allow host |\n| 10 | `9ca16f12` | Mai Chien | Fix port |\n\n**Các thành tựu chính:**\n- ✅ loginByTokenApi khôi phục sau backend refactor\n- ✅ API endpoints đồng bộ `/v1` prefix với backend\n- ✅ User profile persistence qua localStorage\n- ✅ Docker/Vite hotfixes (port, allow host)\n- ✅ Lint cleanup + code style standardization\n- ✅ Stadium calendar edit — hotfix production\n\n---\n\n### 4. ĐÁNH GIÁ TỔNG QUAN\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  🌐 AHV DTLX — Ecosystem Status Report         │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  Backend:     🔄 REFACTORING (Clean Arch P1)   │\n│  Frontend:    ✅ API SYNCED + BUG FIXED        │\n│  Confluence:  ✅ 10 specs ACTIVE               │\n│  Open MR:     ⚠️  1 pending (BE Clean Arch)   │\n│  Last commit: 2026-03-13 (BE & FE)            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Điểm mạnh:**\n- Backend đang tiến tới clean architecture (presentation/api layer)\n- Auth security được nâng cấp (httpOnly cookies)\n- API docs hoàn chỉnh qua Swagger\n- Frontend-Backend API đã sync đúng\n\n**Cần theo dõi:**\n- ⚠️ MR !166 (Clean Arch Phase 1) cần review + merge\n- ⚠️ Last activity: 2026-03-13 (~1 tháng trước) — cần confirm trạng thái hiện tại\n- ⚠️ DTLX Backend + Frontend **chưa có workspace** trong v4-ecosystem-review\n\n**Khuyến nghị:**\n1. Review + merge MR !166 (Clean Arch) trước\n2. Tạo workspace `ahv-dtlx-backend` và `ahv-dtlx-frontend` trong v4-ecosystem\n3. Kích hoạt subagent `senior-backend` + `senior-frontend` cho DTLX\n\n---\n\nReport hoàn tất. Cần tôi làm gì tiếp theo?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":69530,"output":2014,"totalTokens":120438,"cacheRead":25054,"cacheWrite":23840,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775992522250,"responseId":"062ab1cbdb85ca8d2d5ddce594516426","__openclaw":{"id":"4ba736b7","seq":22}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:05e6701d-36aa-491c-ab9d-8edd7eeb37f8","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"ahv-qlhv:merge:fe","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776002693337,"sessionId":"ad3bea85-2fdb-4f14-99f3-c964588a9b39","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776002690782,"endedAt":1776004152498,"runtimeMs":1461716,"thinkingLevel":"medium","lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/ad3bea85-2fdb-4f14-99f3-c964588a9b39.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:ce81d04d-cc26-4b7d-82f4-704a8256c73b","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","label":"ahv-qlhv:merge:be","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1776002693327,"sessionId":"a257979c-3e1e-4845-b903-2fcf80d8a83e","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"status":"failed","startedAt":1776002690642,"endedAt":1776004152478,"runtimeMs":1461836,"thinkingLevel":"medium","lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/a257979c-3e1e-4845-b903-2fcf80d8a83e.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776001662056,"sessionId":"7ae3b683-0b91-4427-abbe-b78ef94eb140","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":52769,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776001583222,"endedAt":1776001660123,"runtimeMs":76901,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/7ae3b683-0b91-4427-abbe-b78ef94eb140.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me summarize for Khuowgn."},{"type":"text","text":"**Tất cả 34 master hoạt động ✅** — đây là tình trạng chi tiết:\n\n---\n\n## 🟢 Tổng quan\n\n```\nopenclaw.json:  ✅ Active (53KB, binded 34 agents)\nworkspaces2/:   ✅ 34/34 workspace tồn tại\nbindings:       ✅ 34 Telegram bots đã bind\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 Theo Model\n\n| Model | Số agent | Trạng thái |\n|---|---|---|\n| `AHV-Holding-DEV` (mạnh) | **15** | ✅ Sẵn sàng |\n| `AHV-Holding-TroLy` (yếu) | **19** | ⚠️ Cần nâng cấp |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Agents dùng model yếu (19)\n\n```\nsenior-backend, senior-frontend, senior-architect, senior-devops,\nsenior-qa, senior-security, code-reviewer, security-reviewer,\ndatabase-reviewer, database-schema-designer, shadcn-expert,\ntypescript-reviewer, refactor-cleaner, coding-standards,\nclean-code, stitch-loop, playwright-pro, realistic-seeder,\nui-design-system\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Agents dùng model mạnh (15)\n\n```\nmaster-orchestrator, prompt-optimizer, planner, epic-design,\nagile-product-owner, market-intelligence, product-strategy,\ncontent-strategy, product-marketing-context, ai-seo, seo-audit,\nstitch-design, ui-ux-pro-max, harness-optimizer,\nperformance-optimizer\n```\n\n---\n\n**Cần tôi upgrade toàn bộ 19 agents sang `AHV-Holding-DEV` không?** Hiện tại hệ thống vẫn chạy được — chỉ là các agent yếu sẽ chậm hơn và dễ gặp lỗi hơn."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":281,"output":442,"totalTokens":53211,"cacheRead":50493,"cacheWrite":1995,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776001650373,"responseId":"062ad5735c4371da617035ab9054974e","__openclaw":{"id":"8c0485a8","seq":49}}]},{"key":"agent:prompt-optimizer:telegram:group:-5168104492","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:-5168104492","accountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot"},"updatedAt":1775990629434,"sessionId":"731cf84b-b802-4c4a-90b9-2fb6c1177f22","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":20343,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775990537840,"endedAt":1775990629120,"runtimeMs":91280,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:-5168104492","lastAccountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/731cf84b-b802-4c4a-90b9-2fb6c1177f22.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can see the full ecosystem. No `qlhv` found in memory. Let me now analyze the prompt and produce the optimization output.\n\nLet me now run the full Phase 0-5 analysis and produce the output.\n\n**Project Detection:**\n- AGENTS.md exists (confirmed via context)\n- No package.json detected (empty dir listing - this is a skills workspace, not a code project)\n- Tech stack: **unknown** — no code files detected in current workspace\n\n**Intent Detection:**\n- Keywords: \"đánh giá\", \"báo cáo\", \"match database\", \"logic chưa khớp\", \"vấn đề\"\n- Category: **Review** + **Research** — a system audit/evaluation task\n"},{"type":"text","text":"## ⚙️ Prompt Diagnosis\n\n### Prompt gốc:\n> *\"master thực hiện triển khai yêu cầu đánh giá, báo cáo cho tôi chi tiết về hệ thống qlhv này xem là có match database với master chưa, có phần logic nào chưa khớp hay có những vấn đề gì\"*\n\n---\n\n### Strengths\n- ✅ Mục tiêu rõ: đánh giá hệ thống `qlhv` — so khớp DB + logic\n- ✅ Có yêu cầu báo cáo chi tiết\n\n### Issues\n\n| Issue | Impact | Suggested Fix |\n|-------|--------|---------------|\n| Không chỉ rõ **hệ thống qlhv** nằm ở đâu (repo, đường dẫn, project) | Agent không tìm được codebase → trả lời sai hoặc thừa | Cung cấp repo path hoặc workspace chứa hệ thống qlhv |\n| Không chỉ rõ **\"master\"** là ai — là agent `@master-orchestrator`, một repo cụ thể, hay branch/commit? | Routing nhầm → sai agent | Chỉ rõ agent phụ trách hoặc source of truth |\n| Không có **acceptance criteria** — khi nào thì báo cáo đủ? | Kết quả mở, không biết dừng ở đâu | Thêm tiêu chí đánh giá cụ thể |\n| Không phân biệt **database nào vs database nào** — so khớp cái gì? | Không rõ scope so sánh | Liệt kê schema cần so sánh (source DB vs target DB) |\n| Không chỉ rõ **output format** — báo cáo dạng bảng, markdown, issue list? | Không đồng nhất | Chỉ rõ format: markdown / Confluence / file |\n| Không chỉ rõ **phạm vi logic** — là tầng nào (API, service, repository)? | Kiểm tra lan man hoặc thiếu | Giới hạn: chỉ logic nghiệp vụ + database layer |\n\n---\n\n## Recommended Components\n\n| Type | Component | Purpose |\n|------|-----------|---------|\n| Orchestrator | `@master-orchestrator` | Điều phối cross-domain review, giao việc cho các agent chuyên biệt |\n| Skill | `@database-schema-designer` | So khớp schema, phát hiện missing/extra fields, FK constraints |\n| Skill | `@senior-backend` | Review logic nghiệp vụ, API contracts, service layer |\n| Skill | `@coding-standards` | Kiểm tra naming, patterns, DRY/KISS compliance |\n| Skill | `@senior-security` | Phát hiện vấn đề bảo mật trong DB access |\n\n---\n\n## Optimized Prompt — Full Version\n\n```\n## Task: Đánh giá & Báo cáo Hệ thống QLHV — So khớp Database & Logic\n\n### 1. Ngữ cảnh\n- Hệ thống: QLHV (Quản lý Học viên)\n- Vị trí codebase: <CHỈ_RỜI_ĐƯỜNG_DẪN_REPO_QLHV>  ← THAY BẰNG PATH THỰC TẾ\n- Database nguồn (source): <TÊN_DB_QLHV>  ← VD: MongoDB collection \"students\", \"courses\"\n- Database master (target): <TÊN_DB_MASTER>  ← VD: MongoDB collection \"students\", \"courses\"\n- Tech stack phát hiện: <AUTO_DETECT_HOẶC_CHỈ_RỖ>\n\n### 2. Mục tiêu\nSo khớp hệ thống QLHV với master, phát hiện:\n  a) **Database mismatch** — thiếu field, thừa field, sai kiểu dữ liệu, FK orphan\n  b) **Logic misalignment** — business rules không đồng nhất giữa service layer vs DB\n  c) **Vấn đề tiềm ẩn** — security holes, missing validations, edge cases chưa xử lý\n\n### 3. Workflow thực hiện\n\n**Bước 1 — @database-schema-designer**\n  → Dump schema của cả 2 database (source QLHV + master)\n  → So sánh field-by-field, type, constraints, indexes\n  → Output: Bảng diff schema (field mới / thiếu / sai type)\n\n**Bước 2 — @senior-backend**\n  → Review logic nghiệp vụ trong service layer của QLHV\n  → Kiểm tra API endpoints: request/response contract có match DB schema không\n  → Output: Danh sách logic chưa khớp hoặc thiếu validation\n\n**Bước 3 — @senior-security**\n  → Kiểm tra truy vấn DB: có SQL/NoSQL injection không?\n  → Kiểm tra quyền truy cập, auth enforcement\n  → Output: Danh sách rủi ro bảo mật (nếu có)\n\n**Bước 4 — @master-orchestrator**\n  → Tổng hợp kết quả từ Bước 1–3\n  → Phân loại: 🔴 Critical / 🟡 Warning / 🟢 OK\n\n### 4. Output format (bắt buộc)\n\n#### 4.1 Database Diff Table\n| Schema | Collection/Table | Field | Type (QLHV) | Type (Master) | Status |\n|--------|-----------------|-------|-------------|---------------|--------|\n\n#### 4.2 Logic Issues List\n| # | Module | Issue | Severity | Recommendation |\n|---|--------|-------|----------|----------------|\n\n#### 4.3 Security Issues List\n| # | Endpoint/Function | Issue | CVSS-like | Fix |\n\n#### 4.4 Summary\n- Tổng số mismatch: X\n- Tổng số logic issue: Y\n- Tổng số security issue: Z\n- ✅ Có thể proceed hay ❌ Cần fix trước\n\n### 5. Ràng buộc\n- Không sửa code — chỉ đánh giá và báo cáo\n- Không modify database production\n- Nếu repo không tìm thấy → báo lỗi ngay và hỏi lại path\n\n### 6. Deliverable\n- Báo cáo hoàn chỉnh dạng Markdown\n- Đăng lên Confluence page nếu có QLHV workspace\n\n```\n\n---\n\n## Optimized Prompt — Quick Version\n\n| Intent | Quick Pattern |\n|--------|--------------|\n| Review | `@master-orchestrator — đánh giá hệ thống QLHV. So khớp DB + logic vs master. Báo cáo table format: diff schema / logic issues / security. Không sửa, chỉ report.` |\n\n---\n\n## Enhancement Rationale\n\n| Enhancement | Reason |\n|-------------|--------|\n| Chỉ rõ repo path + collection/table | Agent biết đâu là source để review — tránh hallucinate |\n| Phân tách Bước 1–3 theo skill chuyên biệt | Đảm bảo mỗi góc nhìn được expert xử lý (DB ≠ logic ≠ security) |\n| Output table format bắt buộc | Lead nhận được artifact đồng nhất, không phải text tự do |\n| Phân loại severity (Critical/Warning/OK) | Lead có thể prioritize action ngay |\n| Không sửa, chỉ report | Đảm bảo agent không tự ý thay đổi production — đúng scope review |\n\n---\n\n> ⚠️ **Missing Info cần bạn cung cấp thêm:**\n> 1. **Repo/workspace chứa hệ thống QLHV** nằm ở đâu?\n> 2. **Tên database + collection/table** cần so khớp là gì?\n> 3. **Branch/commit master** nào là source of truth?\n> 4. **Output đích** — gửi ở đâu (Telegram/Confluence/file)?\n> 5. **Confluence space** có sẵn cho QLHV không?\n\nCung cấp thêm thông tin trên → prompt sẵn sàng paste vào agent để thực thi ngay."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":298,"output":2220,"totalTokens":22563,"cacheRead":15219,"cacheWrite":4826,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775990590009,"responseId":"062aaa3ea767173804f105306e5622f6","__openclaw":{"id":"7a8098b4","seq":8}}]},{"key":"agent:prompt-optimizer:subagent:0eb3c914-87cc-4bdd-9ee9-20aa3e6473e1","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775990263239,"sessionId":"f3fea8c0-f2eb-474e-9c08-b41766f765ad","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"status":"failed","startedAt":1775990261918,"endedAt":1775990286627,"runtimeMs":24709,"thinkingLevel":"medium","lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/f3fea8c0-f2eb-474e-9c08-b41766f765ad.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:prompt-optimizer:telegram:slash:6053576134","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"prompt-optimizer_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775990178347,"sessionId":"0d74c438-5460-4bbd-824a-3bdd04655170","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/prompt-optimizer/sessions/0d74c438-5460-4bbd-824a-3bdd04655170.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:security-reviewer:subagent:6739034d-567f-4c51-8557-f54f81ff565a","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:security","displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982753509,"sessionId":"e0e07a8e-f0f4-4d34-8038-1a225b7374b9","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":56248,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775981729596,"endedAt":1775982220900,"runtimeMs":289559,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/security-reviewer/sessions/e0e07a8e-f0f4-4d34-8038-1a225b7374b9.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The security audit report has been written. Let me provide a summary of what I accomplished."},{"type":"text","text":"**Security audit complete.** Report written to `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews/security.md`.\n\n## Summary of Findings\n\n**6 Critical vulnerabilities** identified:\n1. **Unauthenticated `/device` endpoint** — attendance records can be injected by anyone, no machine key enforced\n2. **IDOR in `/niko-wallets/:id`** — any user's wallet balance readable by any authenticated user\n3. **IDOR in `/employees/:id`** — `verifyAdminOrOwner` not applied to the route\n4. **IDOR in `/leave-requests/:id`** — leave data readable without ownership check\n5. **Hardcoded department bypass** — users in a specific department code get silent admin access (`author.middleware.ts`)\n6. **Swagger `/docs` unauthenticated** — full API surface exposed to anyone\n\n**5 High risks** including missing rate limiting on login, default `123456` password fallback, refresh token cookie always `secure: false`, and inconsistent token version checking in the auth flow.\n\n**9 Medium risks** covering missing Helmet headers, regex injection via unsanitized query params, missing manager checks on leave approvals, permissive CORS defaults, and no audit logging for sensitive operations.\n\n**Priority fix list** with 16 items ranked P1→P4 with estimated fix times included for the dev team."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":109,"output":306,"totalTokens":56554,"cacheRead":48784,"cacheWrite":7355,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775982210718,"responseId":"062a89841dc420b8807b887134a52249","__openclaw":{"id":"5399cca6","seq":91}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:slash:6053576134","kind":"group","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982751128,"sessionId":"6a51c044-d28f-4cc2-be6d-6db8bd5acfcb","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/6a51c044-d28f-4cc2-be6d-6db8bd5acfcb.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:performance-optimizer:subagent:57b179b5-c044-4440-ac46-e970badda4d1","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:perf","displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982557171,"sessionId":"a902b029-cfae-418d-ac58-4d68cb1ca5a0","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":43897,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775981793156,"endedAt":1775982039029,"runtimeMs":0,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/performance-optimizer/sessions/a902b029-cfae-418d-ac58-4d68cb1ca5a0.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"totalTokens":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1775982312919,"errorMessage":"500 {\"error\":{\"message\":\"Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'providerSpecificData')\"}}","__openclaw":{"id":"e06d91db","seq":118}}]},{"key":"agent:senior-backend:subagent:31b6b412-927a-481a-b157-d89c2dd3a187","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:backend","displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982553195,"sessionId":"0422c8f1-54e8-4098-96d7-131e770d87a6","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":37399,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775981666165,"endedAt":1775982025693,"runtimeMs":0,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-backend/sessions/0422c8f1-54e8-4098-96d7-131e770d87a6.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:senior-frontend:subagent:fd28add5-35bd-45b1-8ac5-93bd476867bc","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:frontend","displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982551667,"sessionId":"0e098905-af37-4aff-ba86-64361ef9f7e0","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":60655,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775981825289,"endedAt":1775982551231,"runtimeMs":553833,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/senior-frontend/sessions/0e098905-af37-4aff-ba86-64361ef9f7e0.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The review has been written successfully. Let me provide a summary of what I found."},{"type":"text","text":"The frontend review is complete. Here's what I accomplished:\n\n## Summary\n\nI reviewed the **AHV HRM Frontend** (GitLab project 78077037, `develop` branch) by reading 30+ source files including:\n- `AppRouter`, `ProtectRouter`, `GuardRoute`, `PublicRoute`\n- `baseApi`, `store`, `notificationSlice`, `themeSlice`, `roleApi`\n- All module pages: Employees, Attendance, OKRs, Checkins, Niko, Payrolls, Shifts, Leave Requests, Contracts, Dashboard, Settings\n- Key components: MainLayout, Sidebar, Topbar, AccessControl, FilterCard\n- Services: authApi, employeeApi, nikoApi, checkinApi, payrollApi\n- Configs: AppThemeProvider, socket, constants\n\n### Key Findings:\n\n**STRENGTHS**: RTK Query with token refresh, granular permission system (GuardRoute + AccessControl), lazy loading, dark mode, real-time Socket.io, reusable FilterCard/DebouncedSearchInput components.\n\n**CRITICAL ISSUES**:\n- **Checkins module is broken** — has services & types but NO page component\n- **Extensive `any` types** throughout all pages\n- **Fragile user data extraction** in `usePermission` (4 different OR-chain response shapes)\n- **Pagination hardcoded per page** (10, 12, 50 — not using `PAGINATION_CONFIG`)\n- **Placeholder pages** (Chat, Assets, Evaluations) committed to main\n\n**Missing vs Confluence**: Chat (placeholder, not wired), Bảng xếp hạng (partial/embedded), Khen thưởng nâng cao (missing), Lịch sử checkin chi tiết (missing).\n\nThe full review with 18 prioritized fixes is at `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews/frontend.md`."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":110,"output":425,"totalTokens":61080,"cacheRead":55856,"cacheWrite":4689,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775982537456,"responseId":"062a8acad1d1ca95e8499a31a2100137","__openclaw":{"id":"8309b1ab","seq":117}}]},{"key":"agent:database-reviewer:subagent:51a096dc-1f97-4452-938a-8b629dc4e57e","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:database","displayName":"telegram:g-maiychrus25-company-.ltd","parentSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram"},"updatedAt":1775982403912,"sessionId":"d2dd5ee9-c51e-4197-9153-c47bea577c94","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":11995,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1775981761686,"endedAt":1775981862329,"runtimeMs":31667,"thinkingLevel":"medium","abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/database-reviewer/sessions/d2dd5ee9-c51e-4197-9153-c47bea577c94.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I’m ready to perform the MongoDB design review for the AHV Works system. To deliver a precise, actionable report, I’ll need to access the GitLab project and read all model files as you described. Since I can’t reach external systems directly from here, please confirm that I should proceed by either:\n\n- You providing me with the relevant model files or a downloadable snapshot, or\n- Granting me access (or a temporary token) to read the GitLab BE project 78077025 via the API you cited, so I can pull the files and run an automated analysis.\n\nIf you approve, I will produce the requested artifact with the following structure:\n\n- STRENGTHS\n  - Concise bullets highlighting solid design decisions (e.g., clear bounded contexts, consistent naming, appropriate data typing observed in models, good use of references where appropriate).\n\n- CRITICAL ISSUES\n  - Any showstoppers or major security/data integrity risks (e.g., missing required fields, lack of unique indexes on critical identifiers, no guards against duplicate users, data migration pitfalls).\n\n- HIGH ISSUES\n  - Important concerns that could impact production (e.g., missing compound indexes for high-traffic queries, suboptimal relationship patterns that could cause hot reads, improper use of arrays in heavily updated documents).\n\n- MEDIUM ISSUES\n  - Moderate risks or improvements (e.g., optional fields that should be mandatory for consistency, small normalization opportunities, potential shard-key considerations).\n\n- RECOMMENDATIONS\n  - Concrete, actionable changes grouped by area (schema design, indexing strategy, relationships, data integrity, migrations, operational surveillance, security).\n\n- PRIORITY FIX LIST\n  - A ranked list of fixes with rationale and suggested owners/timeframes.\n\n- ADDITIONAL ANALYSIS (optional)\n  - Compare against Confluence AW space requirements:\n    - Schema completeness for Confluence specs: chat, khen thuong, bang xep hang, lich su checkin\n    - Expected conventions for Confluence-related data (namespaces, collections, indexes)\n  - Scalability probes for large collections:\n    - attendances, checkins, systemLogs\n    - Recommendations on sharding strategy, index patterns, TTLs, archival plans\n\nWhat I will deliver once I have access:\n- A complete, well-structured database.md at /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/reviews/database.md with the exact sections and high-quality observations.\n- Clear evidence-backed findings tied to model files and queries observed in src/modules/*/models/* and src/common/models/*.\n- If gaps exist in the Confluence-spec coverage, I’ll detail what’s missing and propose concrete schema additions.\n\nIf you want me to proceed without providing external access, I can still draft a provisional report template and placeholders, but it will be based on assumptions rather than live code inspection. Let me know which path you prefer, and please share any constraints (e.g., sensitivity, required privilege level, or deadlines)."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":11995,"output":750,"totalTokens":12745,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775981830687,"responseId":"DTkIYYQHlv9px8Wyr3gicVbTQrW2S","__openclaw":{"id":"7bda30cd","seq":3}}]},{"key":"agent:code-reviewer:subagent:370ec3dd-07f8-4a08-a4d6-823d773bfe5b","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","spawnedBy":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728","label":"ahv-works:review:code","displayName":"telegram: