{"type":"message","id":"c676217b","parentId":"05e2d25c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:02:08.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the group session is `agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5212380728` and its session key is `cd565305-b67d-435b-a70a-d2566d0770a6`. The last activity was a heartbeat at 21:55 UTC. Let me try to send the message through a cron job with delivery mode \"announce\" instead, since sessions_send keeps timing out.\n\nActually, looking at the cron session, it says it's for the daily briefing and it's `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"`. The cron job itself should deliver the briefing. Let me check if the cron job exists and what its delivery settings are.","thinkingSignature":"bfbbf82b330f650b679606eadbab69812a0fad540b8c996cdff555f37e7f7e38"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wd0vnna4z41f_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"runs","jobId":"53c5832a-eecc-4d6b-a4c3-d1b78a430dca"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":17166,"output":202,"cacheRead":17433,"cacheWrite":405,"totalTokens":35206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776031319758,"responseId":"062b4958a1ed96ca8efcaafabfdf7418"}}
