{"type":"message","id":"34ae6384","parentId":"3752c792","timestamp":"2026-04-12T22:02:16.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job hasn't run yet (no entries). But the task says to return plain text and it will be delivered automatically. Let me just output the briefing text. The cron job should handle delivery.","thinkingSignature":"deda6f7528c64b50fba2d8dae26a13799ce60b7396cdc8a994de9106c760590a"},{"type":"text","text":"📋 **DAILY BRIEFING — Apr 12, 2026**\n🌐 Orbis Global Orchestrator\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🗓️ **YESTERDAY — SATURDAY APRIL 11**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n✅ **v4 Ecosystem Migration — COMPLETE**\n• 34-agent ecosystem fully deployed\n• All agent configs, SKILL_GATES, DEV_GATE wired up\n• Ecosystem backup archived (`ecosystem-backup-2026-04-11/`)\n• QLHV backend: 4 commits — performance hardening, mobile sidebar, startup fix\n\n✅ **Operations Stable**\n• Daily Briefing cron (5AM UTC+7) — Active ✅\n• 5-Minute Progress cron — Active ✅\n• Telegram token issues — Resolved ✅\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🎯 **TODAY — SUNDAY APRIL 12**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🔴 **Active**\n1. **Stitch MCP Wrapper Testing** — Verify async polling after gateway restart stabilizes\n2. **Stitch `stitch-connect` Skill Update** — Migrate from OAuth to MCP wrapper\n3. **AHV Works: HRM & Landing Page** — Feature review pending\n\n⚡ **Ready to Spawn**\n• `senior-frontend` — UI tasks queued\n• `senior-devops` — Infrastructure checks\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n⚠️ **BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🟡 **Watch:** Stitch MCP wrapper test pending gateway stability confirmation\n🟢 No hard blockers\n🟢 No security incidents\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🌐 **PIPELINE STATUS: HEALTHY**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nAgents Online: 34 | Active Cron: 2 | Sessions: Clean ✅\n\n— *Orbis 🌐*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":161,"output":402,"cacheRead":17766,"cacheWrite":1733